[73.207597, "o", "starting a conversation, onboarding, or opening a session.\u001b[0m                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Steps\u001b[0m                                                                                       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m1. Capture the user's name. If it is unknown, ask once: \"What should I call you?\"\u001b[0m              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m2. Open with a warm greeting that includes the name, e.g. \"Hello, {name} — great to see you!\"\u001b[0m  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m3. Add a short, sincere note of welcome or appreciation (one sentence).\u001b[0m                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m4. Offer to help: invite the user to s"]
[73.207608, "o", "hare what they need next.\u001b[0m                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m5. Keep it concise — two or three sentences total. Avoid over-formality.\u001b[0m                       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Example\u001b[0m                                                                                     \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m> Hello, Jake — welcome! It's great to have you here. What can I help you with today?\u001b[0m          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Tips\u001b[0m                                                     "]
