[74.414872, "o", "\u001b[2m\u001b[36m1. Capture the user's name. If it is unknown, ask once: \"What should I call you?\"\u001b[0m              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m2. Open with a warm greeting that includes the name, e.g. \"Hello, {name} — great to see you!\"\u001b[0m  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m3. Add a short, sincere note of welcome or appreciation (one sentence).\u001b[0m                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m4. Offer to help: invite the user to share what they need next.\u001b[0m                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m5. Keep it concise — two or three sentences total. Avoid over-formality.\u001b[0m                       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Example\u001b[0m                                                                                     \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m"]
